<body>
<div type="letter">
  <pb/>
  <opener><lb/>Al <abbr>S.<hi rend="sup">r</hi></abbr> Daniel Bernoulli</opener>
  <p><lb/>Io non voglio che <abbr>V .S. Ill.<hi rend="sup">mà</hi></abbr> mi scemi
  <lb/>in parte veruna il contento di servirLa<del>[...]</del>
    <lb/><del>[...]</del><add>C</add>he importa che il <abbr>S.<hi rend="sup">r</hi></abbr> <rs type="person">Niccolò</rs> di Lei Fratello, e
  <lb/>mio riverito Padrone, diriga a me le di
  <lb/>Lei lettere? se io fossi à Basilea, non
  <lb/>avrei riguardo <add>alcuno</add> à farne dirigere cento à Lei. Per
  <lb/>l'avvenire poi La prego à scrivermi senza
    <lb/>exordi<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice> e senza perrorazioni; farò così io
  <lb/>pure <del>[...]</del>: e seguiremo anco nelle lettere il metodo
  <lb/>dei buoni amici.<del>[...]</del>
  <lb/><add>Occluso ritrovera un'</add> articolo da aggiungersi alla consaputa mia
  <lb/>lettera: io spero che Ella pure sarà d'accordo
  <lb/>delle due conclusioni segnate di rosso: poste
  <lb/>quelle, il mio sistema susiste. Ed' in verità
  <lb/>non vedo che possa nel mio stistema restar
  <lb/>mai, ò sotto il Polo, o sotto l'Equatore,<del>[...]</del>
  <lb/>asciutto il fondo del Mare. Se vi ci resta
  <lb/>dell'acqua; già le parti mediterranee della 
  <lb/><add>Terra</add> sono più alte delle littorali, ma sono tutti
  <lb/>li Lidi ad' un livello stesso, ne acuno hà
  <lb/>ancora veduto cosa vi sia sotto li <del>[...]</del><add>P</add>oli: si
  <lb/>potrà adunque salvare l'ineguaglianza della
    <pb/>
  <lb/>figura del Mare, l'ineguaglianza (dico) della
  <lb/>figura del Mare, che nascesse dalle cose poste
  <lb/>nel mio sistema.<del>[...]</del> <add>La somma sincera stima, che fò del</add>
  <lb/><del>[...]</del> <add>di Lei sapere, mi <add>rende cara la</add> communicazione <del>[...]</del><add>delli miei</add></add>
  <lb/><del>[...]</del><add>pensieri con Lei: e bramo di <del>[...]</del>veder ben presto,</add> se Ella sia d'accordo meco,
  <lb/>ò almeno non molto lontano. <del>[...]</del><add>S</add>criva <del>[...]</del><add>pure</add>
  <lb/>al margine del mio articolo, che è Padrona.
  <lb/>Del resto le altre parti della lettera saranno
  <lb/>andanti; e <del>[...]</del><add>se</add> possa inserirvi quest'<lb break="no"/>articolo, tutto <add>sarà</add> poi <del>[...]</del>fuori (credo) di
  <lb/>controversia. Quando <choice><orig><g ref="#per">&#42833;</g></orig><reg>per</reg></choice>ò sia <del>[...]</del><add>intieramente</add> scritta; <del>[...]</del><add>La</add>
  <lb/><del>[...]</del> pregherò <add><abbr>V. S. Ill.<hi rend="sup">ma</hi></abbr></add> à dare <del>[...]</del><add>anco</add> à tutta una
  <lb/>occhiata. Mi grazierà di spedire l'occlusa
    <lb/>all'<abbr>Ill.<hi rend="sup">mo</hi></abbr> <abbr>S.<hi rend="sup">r</hi></abbr> suo <rs type="person">Padre</rs> <del>[...]</del><add>co</add>l primo ordinario,
  <lb/>premendomi <del>[...]</del>molto, che Egli veda <add>da me</add> adempito
  <lb/>il dover mio. Mi ami, come fà; mentreche
  <lb/>sinceramente io sono</p>
  <closer><lb/>Di <abbr>V. S. Ill.<hi rend="sup">ma</hi></abbr>
    <lb/><abbr>Di.<hi>mo</hi></abbr> <abbr>Obbl.<hi>mo</hi></abbr> <abbr>ser.<hi>e</hi></abbr> ed'Amico
  <lb/>GPoleni</closer>
</div>
  <pb/>
  <div type="attachment">
    <p>
      <lb/>Fingamus, Tellur<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> solid<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> sphaericae (physice tamen)
      <lb/>figurae esse; eiusdemque section<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> <choice><orig><g ref="#per">&#42833;</g></orig><reg>per</reg></choice> Ax<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice>,
      <lb/><formula>gmTKhrvVg</formula>; t<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> eti<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> fingamus, Tellur<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> ips<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice>
      <lb/>aqua coopert<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> ita, ut su<choice><orig><g ref="#per">&#42833;</g></orig><reg>per</reg></choice>ficiei aquae
      <lb/>sectio sit <formula>PstEpenaP</formula>; nuspiam aut<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> aquae
      <lb/>altitudin<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> lilliaria tria excedere. Sint Poli
      <lb/><formula>P</formula>, et <formula>p</formula>; <choice><orig><g ref="#AE">Æ</g></orig><reg>Ae</reg></choice>quatoris sectio <formula>Ee</formula>; centr<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> <formula>c</formula>.
      <lb/>Praeterea vero ponamur, gravitatis c<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
      <lb/>aliquantillo crescere in progressu ab <choice><orig><g ref="#AE">Æ</g></orig><reg>Ae</reg></choice>quatore
      <lb/>versus Polos; et lineas direction<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> gravi<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
      <lb/>cadenti<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> efficere, ad vicini Poli partes, locutos (qui tamen paucissimis partibus
      <lb/><del>[...]</del><add>deficient a rectis)</add> angulos c<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> lineis tangentibus
      <lb/>su<choice><orig><g ref="#per">&#42833;</g></orig><reg>per</reg></choice>fici<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> curv<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> in punctis, in quibus
      <lb/>sint gravi<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> centra: ita (caussa exempli)
      <lb/>linea <formula>ng</formula> directionis gravis <formula>n efficere</formula>
      <lb/>ad partes vicini Poli <formula>P</formula><choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> angul<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> acut<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> <formula>gnx</formula>
      <lb/>c<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> linea <formula>nx</formula> tangente curv<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> in puncto <formula>n</formula>.</p>
      <p><lb/>Primum dico, grave <formula>n</formula> numqu<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> posse
      <lb/>transire ad partes <formula>t</formula>: portiones enim
      <lb/>fluidi ad utramque Poli plag<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> positae
      <lb/>aequilibrantur: quod igitur de uno quadrante
      <lb/>dicetur, id idem quadantibus conveniet
      <lb/>singulis</p>
      <p><lb/>Deinde vero illus ultro concedo,
      <lb/>paricul<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> quamlibet <formula>n</formula>, si vis movens
      <lb/>urgeat <choice><orig><g ref="#per">&#42833;</g></orig><reg>per</reg></choice> <formula>ng</formula>, mot<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> eti<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> <choice><orig><g ref="#per">&#42833;</g></orig><reg>per</reg></choice>secutur<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice>
      <lb/>secund<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> direction<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> tangentis <formula>nx</formula>, hoc
      <lb/>est accessur<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> versus Plum <formula>P</formula>: dummodo
      <lb/>tamen huiusmodi motioni obstet nulla
      <lb/>alia caussa, nulla afferat impediment<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>.</p>
      <p><lb/>At si particula <formula>n</formula> moveri non poss<del>[...]</del><add>i</add>t,
      <lb/>quia vinceret vim resistent<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> valentior<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice>
      <lb/>semetipsa, c<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> maior<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> ill<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> c<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> su<choice><orig><g ref="#per">&#42833;</g></orig><reg>per</reg></choice>are (ubi
      <lb/>reliqua par<unclear>i</unclear>a sunt) numqu<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> potis esse<!-- Weiser -->
        <pb/>
      <lb/>queat minor vis, sequitur facile, ut
      <lb/>particula <formula>n</formula> motu illo accessus versus
      <lb/>Polum <formula>P</formula> cieri non possit.</p>
      <p><lb/>Nunc huiusmodi impediment<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
      <lb/>clare ut concipiamus; imaginemur, quaeso,
      <lb/>cunctas illas aquae particulas positas
      <lb/>secund<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> line<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> <formula>mn</formula> conniti versus
      <lb/>Polum <formula>P</formula>: deinde animadvertamus, ex
      <lb/>har<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> accessu ad Pol<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> fieri oportere, ut
      <lb/>longius <hi rend="u">a solidae Terrae su<choice><orig><g ref="#per">&#42833;</g></orig><reg>per</reg></choice>ficie
      <lb/>receda<del>[...]</del><add>n</add>t</hi><!-- Die Unterstreichung stammt vermutlich von der Hand von Daniel Bernoulli, ist also nachträglich. Müsste in diesem Fall nicht ausgezeichnet werden, dafür in einer Fussnote kommentiert. --> tot particulae, quot erant
      <lb/>ex positae secund<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> line<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> <formula>mn</formula>. Sed
      <lb/>resistentia, qua particulae illae
      <lb/>nituntur, ne recedant ab ea Terrae
      <lb/>su<choice><orig><g ref="#per">&#42833;</g></orig><reg>per</reg></choice>ficie, maior est conatu, quo hae
      <lb/>particulae positae secund<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> line<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> <formula>mn</formula>
        <lb/>nituntur versus Polus <formula>P</formula><note hand="pers_DE-588-118656503">annotatio 1.<hi rend="sup">a</hi></note> (evidens en<choice><orig><g ref="#im">ī</g></orig><reg>im</reg></choice>
        <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#per">&#42833;</g></orig><reg>per</reg></choice> se est, nisus <choice><orig><g ref="#per">&#42833;</g></orig><reg>per</reg></choice> <formula>P</formula> (evidens en<choice><orig><g ref="#im">ī</g></orig><reg>im</reg></choice>
        <lb/>multo esse maiores nisibus per
        <lb/>tangentes) <choice><orig>Igitur</orig><reg>igitur</reg></choice> particulae positae
        <lb/>secund<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> line<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> <formula>mn</formula> versus Pol<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> <formula>P</formula>
      <lb/>cieri non poterunt.</p>
      <p><lb/>Id tamen, quod propono, ita accipi
      <lb/>vel<choice><orig><g ref="#im">ī</g></orig><reg>im</reg></choice>; non ut, ob directiones <add>tantillo</add> obliquas,
      <lb/>gravitatemque <add>tantillo</add> maior<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> sub Polo, neg<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice>
      <lb/>fieri ull<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> in fluidi figura mutation<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice>:
      <lb/>sed ut affirm<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice>, ab illis directionibus
      <lb/>obliquis, ab illa maiore gravitate sub
        <lb/>Polo, variationes parvas<note type="editorial">"variationes parvas wurde nachträglich von Dan. I B. unterstrichen, da sich seine Randnote auf diese Passage bezieht.</note><note hand="pers_DE-588-118656503"><lb/>variationes tant<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> erunt, donc
          <lb/>directio <formula>ng</formula> sit ad <formula>nx</formula> perpendicu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>laris, seu donec <formula>PC</formula> sit ad <formula>ec</formula> in
        <lb/>reciproca ratione gravitatum:
          <lb/>hoc<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> extra controversiam est, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice><pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>cun<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> fuerit altitudo maris.</note> in fluidi
      <lb/>figur<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> induci; praesert<choice><orig><g ref="#im">ī</g></orig><reg>im</reg></choice> in figur<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice>
      <lb/>aquae maria efformantis; huius en<choice><orig><g ref="#im">ī</g></orig><reg>im</reg></choice>
      <lb/>altitudo exigua est, quippe quae potest<!-- Weiser -->
        <pb/>
      <lb/>solide locis in planisque explorari.</p>
      <p><lb/>Porro si res expendatur diligentius,
      <lb/>serie<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> particular<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> (caussa exempli) positas
      <lb/>secund<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> rectas <formula>ga</formula>, <formula>mn</formula> considerentur
      <lb/>tamqu<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> si esent in cruribus alicuius
      <lb/>vasis, crura habentis communicantia; iam
      <lb/>attentis directionibus <add>(in quibus ponimus; angulos linear<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> direction<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> cum tangentibus pauxillo a rectis deficere)</add> gravitatisque incrementis, exiguis,
        <lb/>inter altitudines <formula>ga</formula>, <formula>mn</formula> earund<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> particular<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice><note hand="pers_DE-588-118656503"><abbr>Ann.</abbr> 2.</note>
      <lb/>haud magna differentia futura esse videtur.
      <lb/>Atque si cogitatione nobis depingamus crus
      <lb/>unum <formula>VP</formula> sub Polo <formula>P</formula>, et alter<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> crus <formula>Te</formula>
      <lb/>sub <choice><orig><g ref="#AE">Æ</g></orig><reg>Ae</reg></choice>quatoris puncto <formula>e</formula> (quae crura
      <lb/>communicent) ex mechanicis profecto non
      <lb/>magn<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> differenti<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> inter altitudines
      <lb/>aquae cruris utriusque re<choice><orig><g ref="#per">&#42833;</g></orig><reg>per</reg></choice>iemus. Quantobr<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice>
      <lb/>illud confirmabitur, a directionibus
      <lb/>gravitatis <add>tantillo</add> obliquis, et a <add>tantillo</add> maiore gravitate in progressu versus
      <lb/><del>[...]</del>Polos parvas mutationes in Mari<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
        <lb/>figuras induci.<note hand="pers_DE-588-118656503"><lb/>H<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c annotatione
        <lb/>mea secunda
        <lb/>refutantur.</note>
        <pb/>
        <figure/>
        <pb type="empty"/>
      <lb/>
